songs.title: A new little tropical song (Starry Eyed)
songs.lyrics:
[Snippet]:
Da da da da da da
Da da da da da da
Baby, da da da da da
Lately, but I see the sun
I know when, I know why
I see a sun
I know when, I know why






I'd like her to sing this that i wrote

Tasting like Pepsi Fire
Cinnamon lips just take me higher
Highs and goodbyes
Your lies and lullabies
National anthem within a ride
My head on your shoulder's side
Your voice is like Elvis's
When he gave Priscilla kisses
Really don't tell
Norman Fucking Rockwell
Blond, red and brown
Take me downtown
Tapes and snippets rewind
Bitch you'rein my mind
Jacqueline, Marilyn and Kennedy
Playing ukelele, hawaiian half-californian baby
The bees and sweet acid velvet shotgun
Mullholland is where we'll be dancing with the sun
Your eyes are starry as the moon
Whisper : '' You're my disco in June ''
